settings.heading:
Image/Text CTA

"Featured Variant" Customization
settings.copy:
You have the option to merchandise this module to have an "Add to Cart" button for a specific product variant.

Step 1: In your settings, scroll down to Featured Variant and select the parent product from the link field.

Step 2: In another tab, visit the Product admin for that product and locate the specific variant you want to populate. Click 'Edit.'

Step 3: In the URL, copy the variant ID that follows "/products/" and paste it into the theme setting here called "Featured Variant".

You should see the product's price and an "Add to Cart" button appear.
